      • createColumnConfigForDataTables

        public java.lang.String createColumnConfigForDataTables()
        Creates the configuration used in the javascript setup for dataTables. The configuration will be inserted into "aoColumns" : [${columnConfigDataTables}] and will determine such things as is the column visible and/or sortable.
        Specified by:

      • createColumnConfigForDataTablesEditable

        public java.lang.String createColumnConfigForDataTablesEditable()
        This method creates the configuration used in the javascript setup for dataTables.editable(). The configuration will be inserted into "aoColumns" : [${columnConfigDataTables}] and will determine such things as column data type.
